{"tid":988503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拼多多現重大BUG被「薅羊毛」 一晚損失200億","createTime":"2019-01-20T06:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T08:12:11.000Z","uid":80481,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"787bc6cbe12ec053e9a7d14ac286d710f845b8c5","tid":988503,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:27:37.000Z","msg":"拼多多現重大BUG被「薅羊毛」 一晚損失200億？<br />\n<br />\n　　新浪科技訊 1月20日午間消息，今天凌晨，拼多多被曝出現重大BUG，用戶可領100元無門檻券。網友稱「有大批用戶開始『薅羊毛』，一晚上200多億都是話費充值」。今天上午9點，拼多多已將相關優惠券全部下架，並私信向「薅羊毛」者表示，此行為已違背服務協議，希望如數歸還，否則將在14個工作日內提起訴訟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15479613648687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15479613648687.jpg&h=7310e991&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　一名參與「薅羊毛」的網友表示，拼多多客服已與其取得聯繫，稱其夜間下單多個虛擬商品，均使用了「100元無門檻抵用券」，這種行為涉嫌違背《拼多多服務協議》且金額較大，希望如數歸還，否則將在14個工作日內提起訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n　　新浪科技查詢了《拼多多服務協議》，在用戶守則第五條寫有：使用拼多多平台外掛或利用拼多多平台當中的BUG來獲得不正當的利益，此舉有損於拼多多和其他用戶的合法權益。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimgs.sina.tw/article/images/news-15479613652586.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimgs.sina.tw%2Farticle%2Fimages%2Fnews-15479613652586.png&h=501a4ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n　　今天凌晨，有網友發現拼多多100元無門檻券存在BUG，大量網友上線「薅羊毛」。從截圖上看，有網友一晚上充值中國移動百餘次，每次為100元，話費0.4元。<br />\n<br />\n　　今天上午9點，拼多多官方緊急將優惠券的領取方式全部下架。拼多多表示，稍後會有官方回應。（韓大鵬）"},{"pid":"92374257e7affe552e9dfecc8fa1775653c218e4","tid":988503,"uid":46943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:33:13.000Z","msg":"睇你有無錢告曬咁多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709816f24469e8a6d44f6d9314f4687895b6def0","tid":988503,"uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"92374257e7affe552e9dfecc8fa1775653c218e4","tid":988503,"uid":46943,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:33:13.000Z","msg":"睇你有無錢告曬咁多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:20:29.000Z","msg":"200幾億抽返一兩億賄賂法院，馬上幫你合併快速開庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a439ce9495db50cbbeae5feb59962f5aedb4c0da","tid":988503,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢app嚟"},{"pid":"290c915baa7de97cb6a05ea30ea466f406b344bc","tid":988503,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa9ab3daf83b04141248bb15b7899a96d53e2e8b","tid":988503,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:36:19.000Z","msg":"【拼多多回應「被薅200億傳言」：實際損失或低於千萬元】針對拼多多因早間漏洞Bug被薅走200億的傳言，拼多多發言人表示，實際最終資損或低於千萬元人民幣。拼多多發言人表示，讓人驚訝的是，比薅羊毛更快的是「資損200億」謠言的傳播速度。<br />\n<br />\n1千萬都比唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946361334eacac4a61bad0534079637385eaae92","tid":988503,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"連登代表： 交你老母稅"},{"pid":"ed548db8274201ac26a54dbcf17d4311b211be34","tid":988503,"uid":1159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n即係咩bug<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ece8a205839d04ef4c5b94c400505ce8607fad","tid":988503,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"留名看贊成豐澤但又屌拼多多"},{"pid":"ca5193dfbbfb743c010058004381fb74317f48c3","tid":988503,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T07:43:51.000Z","msg":"薅係讀茠"},{"pid":"70b0d957d22fbc16cbdba1efb488e51f458820ac","tid":988503,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"11ece8a205839d04ef4c5b94c400505ce8607fad","tid":